author: Giorgio Mendoza
description: The Kiwi DVK is a compact development kit designed for high performance networking and flexible I O expansion. It supports a range of interfaces and slots for prototyping advanced connectivity and power configurations in embedded systems. The DVK is designed to pair with the Kiwi SoM, a compact system on module introduced earlier this year. […]
title: Kiwi DVK Pairs SFP and 2.5GbE with PoE and Modular Expansion for Embedded Development
